# TBD Reforger platform

- Read [`CLAUDE.md`](CLAUDE.md) first — status, run commands, conventions, agent roles.
- **HARD GATE:** Read [`.cursor/rules/cursor-agent-workflow.mdc`](cursor-agent-workflow.mdc) — step phrases, three modes, forbidden code edits.
- **HARD GATE:** [`.cursor/rules/no-silent-deferrals.mdc`](no-silent-deferrals.mdc) — never defer/fold in-scope work unless the operator **explicitly** says to defer that piece.
- Repo root: `$HOME/Projects/TBD-Reforger/` (this checkout may also appear as `/var/home/...` — same tree). Mission Creator specs: `docs/specs/Mission_Creator_Architecture/`.
- Layout: `apps/website/api/` (Axum, pkg `website-api`) · `apps/website/frontend/` (Leptos Trunk, pkg `website-frontend`). Conventions pin: [`docs/platform/WHERE_DOES_X_GO.md`](docs/platform/WHERE_DOES_X_GO.md).
- Frontend surface specs: `docs/website/frontend/` only — never under `apps/**/docs` (verify-doc-layout enforces).
- Ticket source of truth: `.ai/tickets/registry.json`. After edits run `./scripts/ticket sync` and `./scripts/ticket check`. Work on **`main` only** — no `ticket/T-0xx` branches.
- Do not hand-edit generated `docs/TICKET_*.md` or `<!-- ticket-sync:status -->` markers in CLAUDE.md.
- **Cursor:** docs, brainstorm, registry, spec markdown (`executor: cursor-docs` slices).
- **Claude Code:** application code only for slices with `executor: claude-code` (via `./scripts/ticket run`).
- **Executor gate:** stop if active slice is `workbench`, `human`, or `ci` — wait for human completion.
- Git: commit directly to `main` only; tag commits `T-0xx`; end with `Co-Authored-By` trailer.
